              "chord": "",
              "text": "Come to rob my soul of peace."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I’m worn and weary fighting off the grief."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Is there no one who my suffering can relieve?"
